{"TopicId":215267,"ForumId":120,"TopicTitle":"Add option to skip intro on game start","CreatedByName":"Sythosz","CreatedById":227919,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-17T04:42:02Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Sythosz","CreatedById":227919,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-17T04:42:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhen the game is started, the sequence of logos and warnings is absurdly long. Please add a feature to skip these intros?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gargamel","CreatedById":64714,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-17T04:42:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMoved to suggestions. \u00A0\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vortygont","CreatedById":223549,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-17T11:21:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI support this idea\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Nonoo","CreatedById":228016,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-18T19:41:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u002B1\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"TomKerbal","CreatedById":222333,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-21T17:05:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes PLEASE !!!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd/Or load the program in the\u00A0 backround during the intro. It started so super fast before the patch, that was great !\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-03-21T17:08:02Z\u0022 title=\u002203/21/2023 05:08  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003EMarch 21, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by TomKerbal\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"djungelorm","CreatedById":76528,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-24T13:41:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u002B1\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis is particularly annoying when developing mods, where you frequently quit and reload the game. Add unnecessary delay to the code -\u0026gt; compile -\u0026gt; test loop!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Maria Sirona","CreatedById":210882,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-25T15:31:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOkay, but let\u0027s please not have the skip option on the first time it runs bc someone might accidentally skip it \u003Cspan\u003E:c\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}